  "name": "RPlog_The_Capital_s_Underworld_Arrest",
  "title": "The Capital's Underworld: Arrest",
  "summary": "A New Republic task force led by prosecutor Lathan Vel, with the Jedi pilot Leo, Senator Tokoga of Dac, and the medic Myiari, moves to arrest the crime lord Bavon Nass at a restaurant on the capital world. The plan, built around Tokoga's faked death, goes smoothly: Nass is cuffed and charged with placing a bounty on a public official, remaining smugly confident that he will beat the charges and retaliate. At the press conference outside the office, however, a sniper's slug tears through Lathan Vel's throat, and a second sloppy shot nearly hits Nass himself. Chaos erupts as Tokoga pins the cuffed Nass to the ground and Myiari fights through the panicking crowd, ultimately performing heroic medical work to stabilize the dying prosecutor. Nass, ever composed, publicly praises Myiari as the heroine of the hour while being hauled off to his cell, leaving the assassination attempt and his veiled threats hanging over the victory.",
